{"HISTORY":"ColdFusion 9: Added this function.<br>","SYNTAX":"<pre>EntitytoQuery (orm_object, [entity_name]) \r\nEntitytoQuery (orm_object_array, [entity_name])<\/pre><br>","CATEGORY":"ORM functions","PAGENAME":"EntitytoQuery","SEEALSO":"<samp class=\"codeph\"><a href=\"WS32C28934-CDCE-497f-8212-6342141C5846.html\">EntityLoad<\/a><\/samp>, <samp class=\"codeph\"><a href=\"WSC99B2536-9412-4de2-8DE5-34CEBFFF4E93.html\">EntityDelete<\/a><\/samp><br>","DESCRIPTION":"Converts the input entity object or the input array of entity objects to a query object.","LICENCE":"http:\/\/help.adobe.com\/en_US\/ColdFusion\/10.0\/LegalNotices\/index.html","EXAMPLE":"&lt;cfset artists = EntityLoad(&quot;Artist&quot;)&gt; \r\n&lt;cfset artistQuery = EntityToQuery(artists)&gt;<br>","USAGE":"The following conditions apply for this function:<br><li><p>In the case of array input, all objects in the array must be of the same type.<\/p> <\/li> \n<li><p>The result query will not contain any relation data.<\/p> <\/li><br>","Parameter":[]}